parameters: Information Broker Leon: So, is the discussion settled?
Sorceress Sophia: Hehe, would you like a drink first?
Information Broker Leon: I see, so you're being tested, huh?

Information Broker Leon: If I can drink with a beautiful
woman, I'll stick with you until the end, okay?

Information Broker Leon: Hic... You really can hold your
liquor...

Sorceress Sophia: Hehe, could you please talk about the
prince?

Information Broker Leon: I can't do just that... I have my
pride as an information broker, you know...!

Information Broker Leon: I-I can't take it anymore... Sorry,
but please spare me for today... Ugh...

Sorceress Sophia: If there's even a slight possibility that
I couldn't extract information about the prince from that
person, and it could pose a danger...

Sorceress Sophia: It would be quicker to take care of things
here.

Sorceress Sophia: Ugh... Ooh... I, I can't... I, ugh,
anymore...

Sorceress Sophia: I've been with those girls for too long...
If that's the case, I need to find another way... Something
that I can do...

Sorceress Sophia (After all, he's just a man... If his mind
refuses, I should ask his body instead)

Sorceress Sophia (Everything is for that person... Please
forgive me for defiling this body...)

Sorceress Sophia: By the time you sober up, I will have you
tell me everything with your body.
Would you like to skip the adult scene?

Sorceress Sophia (There is a possibility that there is an
entity manipulating this man, so it might be better to go
that route...)
